[base]
# Benchmark Runner
Async execution engine on Tokio. runner.rs orchestrates workers.
connection.rs: deadpool-redis pool (default 50). config.rs: TOML parsing.
worker.rs: sends FT.SEARCH with vector payloads, records latency.

[debug]
Pool exhaustion: RUST_LOG=deadpool=debug. Worker stalls: check INFO commandstats.
Tokio contention: use tokio-console. If p99>>p50: pool contention or server GC.
